{"General": {"Code": "FERGR", "Type": "Common Stock", "Name": "Ferrari Group PLC", "Exchange": "AS", "CurrencyCode": "EUR", "CurrencyName": "Euro", "CurrencySymbol": "\u20ac", "CountryName": "Netherlands", "CountryISO": "NL", "OpenFigi": null, "ISIN": "GB00BN0VZ646", "LEI": null, "PrimaryTicker": "FERGR.AS", "CIK": null, "EmployerIdNumber": null, "FiscalYearEnd": "December", "IPODate": null, "InternationalDomestic": null, "Sector": "Industrials", "Industry": "Integrated Freight & Logistics", "GicSector": null, "GicGroup": null, "GicIndustry": null, "GicSubIndustry": null, "Description": "Ferrari Group PLC provides shipping, integrated logistics, and value-added services for jewelry and precious goods in Europe, Asia, North America, Brazil, and internationally. It offers freight forwarding, ground transportation, and security services; VAT identification services for non-residents; custom solutions and security services for jewelry and watches exhibitions, and trade shows; warehousing services, such as inventory, assembling, and packing services; and tax, hand carry, white gloves, red carpet, and private shopping experience services, as well as on-location services for filming and photo shootings. The company also provides packaging, handling, storage, and insurance solutions for artworks; quality control services, including jewelry checks and general/functional checks for watches; after-sales services; and hallmarking services. Ferrari Group PLC was founded in 1959 and is headquartered in London, the United Kingdom. Ferrari Group PLC is a subsidiary of Deiana Holding Limited.", "Address": "The Kensington Building, London, United Kingdom, W8 5RY", "AddressData": {"Street": "The Kensington Building", "City": "London", "Country": "United Kingdom", "ZIP": "W8 5RY"}, "Listings": {}, "Officers": {"0": {"Name": "Mr. Marco  Deiana", "Title": "CEO & Executive Director", "YearBorn": "1970"}, "1": {"Name": "Mr. Alessandro Nicolo' Ugo", "Title": "CFO & Executive Director", "Yea